---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: tpch_q14"
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |  Projection: Float64(100) * sum(CASE WHEN part.p_type LIKE Utf8("PROMO%") THEN lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount ELSE Int64(0) END) / sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount) AS promo_revenue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   Aggregate: groupBy=[[]], aggr=[[sum(CASE WHEN part.p_type LIKE Utf8("PROMO%") THEN lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount) ELSE Int64(0) END), sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     Inner Join:  Filter: lineitem.l_partkey = part.p_partkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       Filter: lineitem.l_shipdate >= CAST(Utf8("1995-09-01") AS Date32) AND lineitem.l_shipdate < CAST(Utf8("1995-10-01") AS Date32)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |         TableScan: lineitem projection=[l_discount, l_extendedprice, l_partkey, l_shipdate]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |       TableScan: part projection=[p_partkey, p_type]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| physical_plan | SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |   CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |     BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=duckdb compute_context=/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_customer_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_lineitem_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_nation_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_orders_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_part_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_partsupp_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_region_benchmark.db;/tmp/benchmarks/ab17f8/tpch-duckdb_supplier_benchmark.db initial_sql=SELECT ((100.0 * sum(CASE WHEN "part"."p_type" LIKE 'PROMO%' THEN ("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) ELSE 0 END)) // sum(("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")))) AS "promo_revenue" FROM "lineitem" INNER JOIN "part" ON (("lineitem"."l_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey") AND (("lineitem"."l_shipdate" >= CAST('1995-09-01' AS DATE)) AND ("lineitem"."l_shipdate" < CAST('1995-10-01' AS DATE)))) |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
